
                             FLAG CODE 
                http://astro-informatics.github.io/flag
              Fast Fourier-Laguerre transform on the ball
	   Exact spherical Bessel and Fourier-Bessel transforms
  ----------------------------------------------------------------

DESCRIPTION
     The FLAG code provides functionality to perform fast and exact
     Fourier-Laguerre and Fourier-Bessel transforms on the ball.

VERSION
     Release 1.0b1, November 2012

AUTHORS
     B. Leistedt (www.ixkael.com/blog)
     J. D. McEwen (www.jasonmcewen.org)

REFERENCES
     B. Leistedt and J. D. McEwen, Exact Wavelets on the Ball, 
     IEEE Trans. Sig. Proc., 60, 2012 (arXiv:1205.0792)
     
     J. D. McEwen and Y. Wiaux, A novel sampling theorem on the
     sphere, IEEE Trans. Sig. Proc., 59, 2011 (arXiv:1110.6298).

DOCUMENTATION
     See doc/index.html

INSTALLATION
     See documentation

REQUIREMENTS
     SSHT (http://www.spinsht.org)
     FFTW (http://www.fftw.org)

DOWNLOAD
     http://www.jasonmcewen.org/codes.html

SUPPORT
     Please email the authors.

NOTE
     The package is in beta and is still under development.
     Please report problems/bugs by email to: boris.leistedt@gmail.com

